com.ltsllc.miranda.commadline

Class MirandaCommandLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • CommandLine
      • com.ltsllc.miranda.commadline.MirandaCommandLine

  • public class MirandaCommandLine
extends CommandLine
    The arguments to the program.

    Note that the default value for things like the properties filename is null. This means it was absent from the arguments.
